 * @param vectorX 回転軸の方向ベクトルX成分
 * @param vectorY 回転軸の方向ベクトルY成分
 * @param vectorZ 回転軸の方向ベクトルZ成分
 * @param pointX 回転軸が通る点のX座標
 * @param pointY 回転軸が通る点のY座標
 * @param pointZ 回転軸が通る点のZ座標
 *
 * !--- locale=En-US ---
 * Rotates the vector around an axis that passes through the specified point and points in an arbitrary direction.
 * 
 * @param vectorID The ID of the target vector.
 * @param angle The rotation angle, in radians. Positive values rotate in the direction in which a right-handed screw advances along the axis vector.
 * @param vectorX The X component of the axis direction vector.
 * @param vectorY The Y component of the axis direction vector.
 * @param vectorZ The Z component of the axis direction vector.
 * @param pointX The X coordinate of a point on the axis.
 * @param pointY The Y coordinate of a point on the axis.
 * @param pointZ The Z coordinate of a point on the axis.
 */
macro rotVector( int vectorID, float angle, float vectorX, float vectorY, float vectorZ, float pointX, float pointY, float pointZ ){
  SYSTEM_PROCESS_DRIVER_GRAPHICS_rotVector3D( vectorID, angle, vectorX, vectorY, vectorZ, pointX, pointY, pointZ );
}

/**
 * !--- locale=Ja-JP ---
 * 任意点を通る、任意方向ベクトルの回転軸まわりに、ベクトルを回転させます。
 * 
 * @param vectorID 対象ベクトルのID
